    "However, their technical report describes it as a mix of publicly available data and licensed data from third-parties.",
    "Schreiner (2023) reports that the training corpus of GPT-4 has around 13 trillion tokens, including well-known sources such as the CommonCrawl and data from Twitter, Reddit, YouTube, and a large collection of textbooks.",
